<p>如果你使用的是Internet Explorer 9以上的Internet Explorer浏览器则可<input value="点击这里" onclick="window.external.msAddTrackingProtectionList('http://rules.adfiltering-rules.asia/svn/trunk/lastest/rules_for_TPL.tpl','广告强效过滤规则 for TPL');" type="button" />添加订阅到TPL（跟踪保护）中。</p>
<p><img src="index_files/dingyue_TPL.png" alt="" height="250" width="354" /></p></div>
